snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard: Will The Judge Finally Uncover The Truth?
snippet.description:
For weeks Johnny Depp and Amber Heard were battling it out in the British courts during a liabel trial against the parent company of The Sun Newspaper. Many dark moments of their past relationship were brought up when they both testified. What did their close ones and Depp's exes say? Will we finally find out who was right and who was wrong? #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #PiratesOfTheCaribbean
